videos.headline: Sims brushes himself off after barreling into end zone for TD
videos.description: Jeff Sims gives Georgia Tech an early lead with a 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_ONe-PLay (Sims brushes himself off after barreling into end zone for TD) 2020/9/19

videos.headline: Gabriel hits Nixon on the slant for UCF TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel throws a quick pass to Tre Nixon for a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gabriel hits Nixon on the slant for UCF TD) 2020/9/19

videos.headline: Georgia Tech gets a lift in before kickoff
videos.description: Georgia Tech wants to make sure they're ready for the game as they pump some iron before kickoff.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc. (Georgia Tech gets a lift in before kickoff) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gabriel drops dime to Williams for UCF TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel throws the ball behind the defender's head to Marlon Williams for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gabriel drops dime to Williams for UCF TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCrae goes right up the middle for the UCF TD
videos.description: UCF running back Greg McCrae goes right through Georgia Tech's defense for the 21-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCrae goes right up the middle for the UCF TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia Tech and UCF exchange turnovers on back-to-back possessions
videos.description: Georgia Tech gets the fumble recovery on one possession, then on the next, UCF tips the ball in the air and gets the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia Tech and UCF exchange turnovers on back-to-back possessions) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nixon goes up and grabs the UCF TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel goes up top to Tre Nixon for the 25-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nixon goes up and grabs the UCF TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gibbs gets the GT touchdown right before the half
videos.description: Jahmyr Gibbs finds the end zone from nine yards out, cutting the UCF lead to 14 at half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gibbs gets the GT touchdown right before the half) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gibbs breaks free down the sideline for the GT TD
videos.description: Jahmyr Gibbs shows off his speed down the sideline for a 33-yard Georgia Tech touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gibbs breaks free down the sideline for the GT TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anderson does it all for UCF TD
videos.description: Otis Anderson rushes three straight times for 28 yards, getting into the end zone and extending UCF's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Anderson does it all for UCF TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marlon Williams shows out on UCF TD drive
videos.description: Marlon Williams shows off his skills with a sweet catch over the defender and a touchdown catch to extend UCF's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marlon Williams shows out on UCF TD drive) 2020/09/19 ESHEET
